Package semanticMarkup.ling.chunk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IChunker
    IChunker refines the chunking result stored in a ChunkCollector in a bottom-up fashion
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractChunker
    AbstractChunker implements common functionality of an IChunker shared among concret IChunker implementations
    Chunk
    A Chunk has a ChunkType, contains a ordered set of children chunks and may have properties.
    ChunkCollector
    A ChunkCollector stores the root chunk to which a terminal is assigned to for a single sentence.
    ChunkCollectorIterator<T>
    ChunkCollectorIterator allows to iterate over the Chunks of a chunkCollector
    ChunkerChain
    ChunkChain allows to chain a number of IChunkers and execute them consecutively
  • Enum Summary

    ChunkType
    ChunkTypes a Chunk can be of
